Fraud Claim Prediction

  • Objective: Build a predictive model to classify claims as fraudulent or legitimate.
  • Process: Use machine learning algorithms (e.g., Random Forest, Logistic Regression) to train the model on historical claims data, focusing on the suspicious_activity flag.
  • Output: Trained model capable of predicting fraudulent claims.
